{{en-noun|~|laws}}

# {{lb|en|uncountable}} The body of rules and [[standard]]s issued by the legislative body, or to be applied by [[court]]s and [[similar]] authorities.
#: {{ux|en|By '''law''', one is not allowed to own a wallaby in New York City.}}
